Holly Earl https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Holly_Earl 0 Holly Earl (born 31 August 1992) is an English actress. She is best known for her role as Zoe in Cuckoo, Kela in Beowulf: Return to the Shieldlands, Agnes in the Channel 4 Tv series Humans and Nita Clements in the BBC medical drama Casualty.
